The Nigerian Medical Association (NBA) Zamfara State has confirmed the kidnap of one of its members, Dr Mansur Muhammad. A statement on Tuesday, in Gushau by the NMA Chairman, Dr Mannir Bature, said Dr Mansur until his abduction was a Medical Director of the General Hospital in the state. “The unfortunate incidence happened on Saturday, June 25, 2022, at Mashayar Zaki along Dansadau -Magami Road in Zamfara State, ” the NMA confirmed. The statement called on people in the state to intensify prayers and stressed that the association is working tirelessly to ensure the release of their abducted member in the state. The Zamfara Police Public Relations Officer did not pick his calls to give incite into the incident.